# Optional: LLM-powered feedback (OpenAI). If set, analysis uses the model below instead of rule-based logic.
# Get an API key at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#
# Production (e.g. Vercel): add OPENAI_API_KEY under Project → Settings → Environment Variables (Production).
# If it is missing on the server, analysis falls back to rule-based tips (simpler; can look repetitive).
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Optional: Model for resume analysis. Defaults to gpt-4o-mini. Use gpt-4o for higher quality.
# OPENAI_ANALYZE_MODEL=gpt-4o

# Optional: POST JSON events (report email requests, product feedback, course clicks) to your URL — Zapier, Make, Slack webhook, etc.
# If unset, events only appear in server logs as [AppEvent] lines.
# LEADS_WEBHOOK_URL=
